name: IC 400-C Gold
description: MAXEMA® - A Top Italian Brand.  The Icon its design is the perfect synthesis of past, present and future, a design conceived to be the testimony of a message that will last through time. Its essential lines and the delicate harmony of its proportions are the fruit of an aesthetic study that gives Icon an un mistakable style which bespeaks a refined simplicity, always fresh, never hackneyed. Clip and barrel in shiny finishing, with gold tip. Twist-action, made of non-toxic, highly resistant ABS plastic. Galvanic process used to glid ABS tip, jumbo refill available in black or blue ink, up to 2500 metres of writing.
additionalInfo: Italian Design and Make. Exclusive to Dex Collection in Australia and New Zealand.  1,000 units minium per colour.
